WEBVTT

00:03:28.156 --> 00:03:32.037
And those penalties vary --
we're talking $500 fines.

00:03:32.061 --> 00:03:33.264
Five hundred dollars?

00:03:33.288 --> 00:03:34.441
Are you kidding me?

00:03:34.465 --> 00:03:35.821
Women are losing their jobs.

00:03:35.845 --> 00:03:38.152
They're suffering
from damaged relationships

00:03:38.176 --> 00:03:39.537
and damaged reputations.

00:03:39.561 --> 00:03:42.101
They're falling into illness
and depression.

00:03:42.125 --> 00:03:44.613
And the suicide rates are climbing.

00:03:45.802 --> 00:03:49.992
You're looking at a woman
who spent 11 months in court,

00:03:50.016 --> 00:03:52.143
thirteen trips to the courthouse

00:03:52.167 --> 00:03:54.633
and thousands of dollars in legal fees,

00:03:54.657 --> 00:03:56.291
just to get two things:

00:03:56.315 --> 00:03:59.212
a protection from cyberstalking
and cyberabuse,

00:03:59.236 --> 00:04:01.712
otherwise known as a PFA,